TM TT LUN VN
ti: C nhn ho h thng gi vic lm
Tc gi lun vn: c Thi
M s hc vin: 20211260M
Ngi hng dn: TS. Trn Vit Trung
Ni dung tm tt:
a) L do chn ti
Hin nay, cc website tuyn dng trc tuyn tr thnh mt trong nhng knh chnh
mi ngi tm kim vic lm. Nhng nn tng ny tit kim rt nhiu thi gian
v tin bc cho c ng vin cng nh t chc tuyn dng. Tuy nhin, cc k thut truy
xut thng tin truyn thng nh tm kim cng vic mong mun thng qua t kha bng
my tm kim khng cn ph hp. L do l v s lng kt qu tr v cho ngi tm
vic c th rt ln, h cn dnh thi gian ng k c v xem xt cc la chn ca
mnh, dn n tri nghim tm vic rt nhm chn v kh khn.
Chnh v l , lun n ny hng ti mc tiu xy dng mt h thng gi vic lm
hiu qu, tng tnh c nhn ha v mc ph hp ca kt qu tm vic, gip tri
nghim ngi dng v hnh trnh tm vic tr nn d dng v th v hn.
b) Mc ch nghin cu ca lun vn, i tng, phm vi nghin cu.
Mc ch chnh ca ti l nghin cu, xut m hnh cho h gi trong lnh vc
th trng lao ng, phm vi nghin cu: s dng d liu ngn ng ting Anh.
c) Tm tt c ng cc ni dung chnh v ng gp mi ca tc gi
Ni dung v ng gp ca lun vn: (1) ng gp vo s hiu bit chung v th trng
vic lm v hnh vi ca ngi tm vic bng cch phn tch 2 b d liu vic lm:
RecSys2016 v CareerBuilder2012; (2) Nghin cu, trin khai v th nghim cc thut
ton xut cng vic khc nhau; (3) nh gi hiu sut v kh nng s dng ca cc
thut ton trn s dng 2 ch s: Map@K v RSScore.
d) Phng php nghin cu
Cc phng php nghin cu bao gm:
Tm hiu v nghin cu v thc trng d liu v cc phng php tip cn ca
h gi i vi lnh vc vic lm.
Th nghim, nh gi hiu nng v xut m hnh h gi ph hp vi d liu
trong lnh vc vic lm.
e) Kt lun
Trong lun vn ny, tc gi trnh by mt s ng gp cho ti h gi trong lnh vc
vic lm. u tin, tc gi phn tch 2 b d liu vic lm: RecSys2016 v
CareerBuilder2012, qua ng gp vo s hiu bit chung v th trng vic lm v
hnh vi ca ngi tm vic. Th 2, tc gi nghin cu, trin khai v th nghim ng
dng cc thut ton xut i vi th trng lao ng. Cui cng, tc gi nh gi
hiu sut v tnh thc tin ca cc m hnh h gi i vi lnh vc vic lm.
Mt s kt qu nghin cu ca tc gi c lin quan n ti h gi trong lnh vc
vic lm c cng b ti hi ngh trong nc v quc t:
- Cao, H. N., Do, D. T., Tran, V. T., Cao, T. D., & Song, Y. I. (2022, August). Synonym Prediction
for Vietnamese Occupational Skills. In Advances and Trends in Artificial Intelligence. Theory
and Practices in Artificial Intelligence: 35th International Conference on Industrial, Engineering
and Other Applications of Applied Intelligent Systems, IEA/AIE 2022, Kitakyushu, Japan, July
1922, 2022, Proceedings (pp. 351-362). Cham: Springer International Publishing.
